{
  "texts": [
    "In a financial environment, this may mean precisely spotting fraudulent activity.",
    "In ecommerce, it might mean matching a customer inquiry's relevant product category.",
    " Coherence evaluates the model's logical development of output.",
    "Though technically accurate, an inconsistent or conflicting response might nonetheless be confusing.",
    " Relevance ensures that the answer either satisfactorily answers the question or fixes the problem."
  ]
}